<section>
	<h1>Certificate</h1>
	{include file="/obj/byline.tpl"}
	<div class="headingbox">
		<h1><em>the</em> Rule</h1>
		<div class="justify">
			<p>A school, where a minimum of four (4) <a href="{$uri.actions}">Life-Link actions</a> have been reported during a calendar year, will qualify for a Life-Link Certificate.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
<section>
	<p>A Certificate will be printed, signed and sent by mail or email to the qualified schools in February-March for the previous year.</p>
	<p>If your know that your school has reported a minimum of four actions, and you have not received your Certificate, please <a href="{$uri.mail}">email the Life-Link office</a> !</p>
	<p>Show off with your Certificate in visible place around your school so that your Life-Link team gets the recognition that it deserves. And why not have a nice ceremony? Invite local media!</p>
	<h1 class="simple">Be proud of yourselves! We definitely are!</h1>
</section>
